{"tid":2037362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建制送防疫品誘長者簽名","createTime":"2020-05-27T02:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T03:21:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56ac040806cbd63245dab3cc843a921d7cf3f994","tid":2037362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200527/N2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FN2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4%2F&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=012d74a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FN2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4%2F&h=15c3f292\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200527/N2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4/</a><br />\n<br />\n建制送防疫品誘長者簽名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R3WBWRWQBBLQSQJUPW3DI2255U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR3WBWRWQBBLQSQJUPW3DI2255U.gif&h=00a7cef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排隊市民被游說簽名支持國安法。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「香港各界撐國安立法聯合陣線」發起簽名行動，除政府問責官員到場簽名表忠，親中團體亦為北京抬轎。新家園協會昨午在大埔太和邨對開派禮物，民建聯團隊則在場收集支持國安法簽名，多次混入排隊人龍中索取簽名，有長者不知內容簽署，事後始知是撐國安惡法，感覺受騙。有正義街坊懷疑兩個親中團體「打龍通」，無所不用其極索取簽名造勢。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：草案增「活動」擴定罪範圍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩團體同場 僅距兩米<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。，禮品包印有「關愛防疫包」字眼，袋內有數包麵食及少量酒精消毒液，當時有超過20人排隊。僅距兩米，民建聯陳克勤及周浩鼎團隊則發起撐國安法簽名。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。一名婆婆表示，以為簽名才能領取禮物，直言不知道自己簽署了甚麼，對方亦沒有詢問她是否支持國安法，只着她在紙上簽名，「唔知喎，佢叫我簽名之嘛。」另一女街坊表示，自己並不了解國安法，亦不知簽署了贊成立國安法，「我唔係幾清楚，嗰啲我唔識㗎，我唔識字㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n街坊張小姐諷刺新家園協會與民建聯是完美組合，一個派發禮品吸引人群，一個混入人群中索簽名，「唔係用禮物引人簽名，都係誤導老眼昏花嘅長者」。她認為做法鬼祟、卑鄙。就有關指控本報曾聯絡陳克勤、周浩鼎及新家園協會，但未聯絡上。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃麗英<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NAP7SIGT536VJAALQA7SXACP6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNAP7SIGT536VJAALQA7SXACP6Y.jpg&h=6e26e293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n街坊各獲派一袋「關愛防疫包」。黃麗英攝"},{"pid":"fa2b476b4fe58a4aa82af989fa302c2f2c05dfe5","tid":2037362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"[突發集人］5.27 反國法遊行 1300<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fwPHdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fwPHdS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51149ec3e92d4536a4eac340fe7b0dd40dcb422f","tid":2037362,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4e66818f7d7bdc01ab5749615011c82376a76d","tid":2037362,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c80d33b76c7ff10e59b18e17e19614985cba62","tid":2037362,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"算啦，呢d簽名打飛機用，可以無限look簽，跟本可以吹到十幾億人支持惡安法"},{"pid":"426cb881007487cfeb842cb9b88ced6a6806690c","tid":2037362,"uid":109629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"廢老唔死都無用<br />\nanyway是撚但啦 就算佢地得100個簽名咪又係會對外公佈有700萬名香港市民支持國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d89e1ce1f6eb71c4bbb8d82f